## ⚙️ Quick Start
1. Clone this repository: 
   `git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/windows-to-linux-rsync.git`
2. Make the script executable: 
   `chmod +x backup-windows.sh`
3. Update the variables in the script to match your environment.
4. Set up your Cron job: 
   `(crontab -l ; echo "15 14 * * * /path/to/backup-windows.sh") | crontab -`
